        Merge two given Concept. Do not merge if a parameter is invalid.
        Parameters:
        s1 - r if the first Concept should be random, i if its index is specified as the third parameter.
        s2 - r if the second Concept should be random, i if its index is specified as the fourth parameter.
        i1 - the index of the first merged Concept if i was the first parameter.
        i2 - the index of the second merged Concept if i was the second parameter.
        Returns:
        the two merged Concept
